data.name: infoBox.Text
data.value: Information Panel 1. Click the dropdown menus to select cards 2. Click Draw to confirm card selections 3. Cards chosen by the Dealer will be Green 4. You cannot select the same hand twice in the same pattern. 5. Four green cards in two seperate patterns wins the pattern. 6. There are six patterns to win. 4. Click Reset to clear card selections 5. Click Stop to close the application
